column2: The Togo national football team is involved in an attack in Angola, and as a result withdraws from the Africa Cup of Nations.{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/8449611.stm |title=Togo withdraw from Africa Cup of Nations |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2010-01-09 |accessdate=2009-01-09}}
